<div class="patternContent"><div class="patternTopic"> <h1><a name="FSSDataset_Operations"></a>  <strong><noop>FSSDataset Operations</strong> </h1>
<div class="twikiToc"> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Dataset_Operations"> Dataset Operations</a> <ul>
<li> <a href="?cover=print#Defining_Datasets"> Defining Datasets</a>
